{"tid":1153890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士接待1.2萬中國人旅團 瑞士旅遊業界鼓舞：天賜之物","createTime":"2019-05-14T02:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:39:36.000Z","uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5089b8b0f055fc6398d988ff912fc6f8d4cd499e","tid":1153890,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】全球最大直銷公司婕斯（Jeunesse Global）最近組織1.2萬名中國員工進行為期6天的瑞士之旅，是「有史以來到訪瑞士的最大旅遊團」，也成為對這個歐洲小國的巨大考驗。一些當地人抱怨這樣的旅遊團影響他們的生活，但<span style=\"color: red;\">瑞士旅遊業卻歡欣鼓舞，認為「1.2萬名中國人到來是蘇黎世的天賜之物」。 </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbefd1eb2b21df72a6f401d05a8f80956f540034","tid":1153890,"uid":99700,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://38.media.tumblr.com/9fd5c0e79f901414f5694c428b6be74c/tumblr_nnzuxm94Vu1terwlso1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F38.media.tumblr.com%2F9fd5c0e79f901414f5694c428b6be74c%2Ftumblr_nnzuxm94Vu1terwlso1_500.gif&h=cf7dba42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48e43bb0f42f6c90490917424eca8bf2f7cb5e7d","tid":1153890,"uid":253005,"like":1,"dislike":47,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:31:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3044e8bbbc23c992aa1f96a251fae4dc37b72966","tid":1153890,"uid":179409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:34:31.000Z","msg":"遲啲就知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762dc6149a3808ceb09e5034f8e5c4c2e9bdb246","tid":1153890,"uid":39365,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"個個國家旅發局都一定話歡迎任何國家遊客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5667e552636d48de1d0cf66d7117217fa7c4efd0","tid":1153890,"uid":18241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"48e43bb0f42f6c90490917424eca8bf2f7cb5e7d","tid":1153890,"uid":253005,"like":1,"dislike":47,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"reply